        <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Steps to Obtain Your CFI Spin Endorsement</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-700">As part of your journey to become a Certified Flight Instructor, you must demonstrate proficiency in spin recovery techniques. Our program prepares you to handle spins confidently and safely, ensuring you meet all FAA requirements.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700 lg:max-w-none">
          <p>The spin endorsement training typically includes ground instruction and flight training. You will learn the aerodynamics of spins, how to enter and recover from spins, and how to teach these techniques to your students. The duration of the training can vary, but most candidates complete it within a few dedicated training sessions.</p>
          <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-gray-600">
